Mad rush getting ready for the Valentines Market on Sunday @kellysgreenlounge. 
2 to 4 pm 
5323 Main St. in Orono

Coach Alli here guys... it seems to be my turn 😱! I’ve been wanting one for a while now.  And, no it won’t be BOH’s cool logo.  Lol

I was a year old out with my mom and her friend at Woolworth’s (who remembers that original five-and-dime store?) me in my high chair, the tray of hot coffee in front of me hanging over the edge of the table and WHAM!  My happily playing hands went down on the tray and the steaming hot coffee went down my neck and arm.  The restaurant wouldn’t do anything to help for fear of a lawsuit, so I was rushed to hospital in a police car with 3rd degree burns.

It was a bit problematic as a teenager, everyone thought I had a huge hickey on my neck.  It’s part of me, it’s faded now and I barely think of it anymore but I had the thought... what a neat place to put my first tattoo, over my burn!  My baked_on_high_guy gave me a gift certificate for Xmas so I have no more excuses, the time has come... and yes, yes I do plan to be quite high. 💚😉🌿

Are you coming?  We’d love to see you @kellysgreenlounge for a Valentines Market.  BOH will be there with some of our yummy edibles along with other cool vendors.

The month of Love is upon us!

Join Coach Alli, a Relationship Alignment Coach and Author @kellysgreenlounge for her interactive talk, RelationShift; a new paradigm in human relationships.

It’s really relationships that make the world go round.  What would the it look like if we could all just get along better. 
Would you love more connection, intimacy, influence, heat in your most important relationships?  Do you wish some were easier, with less conflict and more team spirit?  Come find out how to transform the relationships you hold most near and dear to you.

The registration price is $10 for this event and preregistration is now open to hold your spot.  To pre-book pm us.
